name: U2DPN
deploy:
version: '2.0'
endpoints:
services:
  minio:
    image: minio/minio:latest
    expose:
      - port: 9000
        as: 9000
        to:
          global: true
      - port: 9090
        as: 9090
        to:
          - global: true
    env:
      - MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=minio9880707009008
      - MINIO_SECRET_KEY=minio1236585895980
      - AWS_DEFAULT_REGION=us-east-1
      - AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=minio
      - AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=minio123

    cmd:
        - /bin/bash
        - -c
    args:
        - server
        - /storage 
        - --console-address=:9090
  
profiles:
  compute:
    minio:
      resources:
        cpu:
          units: 2
        memory:
          size: 20Gi
        storage:
          - size: 100Gi
            attributes:
              persistent: true
              class: beta3
  placement:
    dclound:
      attributes:
        host: subnet
        capabilities/storage/1/class: beta3
      pricing:
        minio:
          token: scu
          max_price: 10000000
          min_price: 1000000
deployment:
  minio:
    dclound:
      profile: minio
      count: 1
